1806
00:41:12,040 --> 00:41:13,640
 dakle, Meseć Manolić je infiltriran.

1807
00:41:13,640 --> 00:41:17,460
 Znači, na sljedećim izborima,

1808
00:41:17,460 --> 00:41:20,400
 kogod ne bude od političara

1809
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:22,020
 koji se bave politikom i stranaka,

1810
00:41:22,020 --> 00:41:23,780
 htio ići na zajedništvo,

1811
00:41:23,780 --> 00:41:24,700
 ja često govorim,

1812
00:41:24,780 --> 00:41:25,300
 i mi razgovorimo.

1813
00:41:25,300 --> 00:41:27,000
 Dakle, moramo se okupiti.

1814
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:27,780
 Ne želi dobra hrvatska.

1815
00:41:27,780 --> 00:41:29,060
 Ako se, da, apsolutno.

1816
00:41:29,060 --> 00:41:31,940
 Ali, a to moraju znati glasači,

1817
00:41:31,940 --> 00:41:33,900
 jer postoje mehanizmi,

1818
00:41:33,900 --> 00:41:34,820
 medijski manipulaciji,

1819
00:41:34,820 --> 00:41:36,160
 se potiče to svađanje,

1820
00:41:36,160 --> 00:41:37,120
 ne zajedništvo i sl.

1821
00:41:37,200 --> 00:41:39,200
 na koncu, nikako da se dogodi

1822
00:41:39,200 --> 00:41:40,620
 da stranke koji imaju

1823
00:41:40,620 --> 00:41:41,680
 temeljne vrijednostne interese

1824
00:41:41,680 --> 00:41:42,300
 da idu zajedno,

1825
00:41:42,300 --> 00:41:43,540
 pa se poslije mogu tući

1826
00:41:43,540 --> 00:41:44,280
 u Saboru, drugdje,

1827
00:41:44,280 --> 00:41:44,760
 u Skupštinu,

1828
00:41:44,760 --> 00:41:45,580
 oko nekih pitanja.

1829
00:41:45,580 --> 00:41:47,040
 Ali, kogod ne bude išao zajedništvo,

1830
00:41:47,040 --> 00:41:48,100
 jel, moja je uvijek preporuka,

1831
00:41:48,100 --> 00:41:49,440
 godinama to pričam,

1832
00:41:49,440 --> 00:41:51,080
 desetljičima i kad nisam bio u politici,

1833
00:41:51,080 --> 00:41:52,680
 zapravo, ili je,

1834
00:41:52,680 --> 00:41:54,340
 što je teoretski jasno,

1835
00:41:54,340 --> 00:41:56,340
 dakle, ili je naša korisna budala

1836
00:41:56,340 --> 00:41:57,420
 koja radi za neprijatelja,

1837
00:41:57,420 --> 00:41:58,720
 ili je strana agentura,

1838
00:41:59,100 --> 00:41:59,920
 Dakle, neprijateljska.

1839
00:41:59,920 --> 00:42:00,900
 Ej, stvarno,

1840
00:42:00,900 --> 00:42:01,720
 ako to uspijemo,

1841
00:42:01,720 --> 00:42:03,760
 zahvaljujući ovakvim podcastima,

1842
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:04,540
 ako to uspijemo,

1843
00:42:04,540 --> 00:42:06,920
 dakle, usvijesti hrvatskih građana

1844
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:08,000
 da ih ne ispiru mozak

1845
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:09,300
 preko ovih bombardiranja,

1846
00:42:09,300 --> 00:42:10,680
 onda je to veliki uspjeh

1847
00:42:10,680 --> 00:42:11,920
 i ići će Hrvatsko zajedništvo.

1848
00:42:11,920 --> 00:42:14,120
 U ostalom, mi to zastupamo...

1849
00:42:14,120 --> 00:42:15,360
 Otvoreno, jasno i javno.

1850
00:42:15,360 --> 00:42:18,240
 Puno bi mi mogli još razgovarati,

1851
00:42:18,240 --> 00:42:20,280
 ali treba još i pojes nešto,

1852
00:42:20,280 --> 00:42:22,760
 treba otići, vratiti se u Zagreb,

1853
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:24,220
 Hrvatska igra večeras.

1854
00:42:25,140 --> 00:42:27,500
 Hvala vam na razgovoru.

1855
00:42:27,500 --> 00:42:28,920
 Biće još puno razgovora

1856
00:42:28,920 --> 00:42:30,400
 i stvarno mi je čas

1857
00:42:30,400 --> 00:42:31,680
 da sam vas imao ovdje

1858
00:42:31,680 --> 00:42:32,840
 i kao hrvatskog branitelja,

1859
00:42:32,840 --> 00:42:34,100
 dragovoljca i profesora

1860
00:42:34,100 --> 00:42:36,700
 i čovjeka koji je od tuđmana

1861
00:42:36,700 --> 00:42:38,280
 do danas je bio u stvaranju

1862
00:42:38,280 --> 00:42:38,940
 u Hrvatske države.

1863
00:42:38,940 --> 00:42:39,480
 Hvala vam, profesor.

1864
00:42:39,480 --> 00:42:40,020
 Evo, zahvaljujem.

1865
00:42:40,020 --> 00:42:41,340
 Stvarno, iskreno,

1866
00:42:41,340 --> 00:42:42,520
 jer smo kolege i prijatelji,

1867
00:42:42,520 --> 00:42:43,460
 dakle, zahvaljujem jer

1868
00:42:43,460 --> 00:42:45,220
 strašno su važne ovakve stvari,

1869
00:42:45,220 --> 00:42:46,940
 dakle, da do hrvatskih građana

1870
00:42:46,940 --> 00:42:48,820
 što više dođe ovakvih stvari

1871
00:42:48,820 --> 00:42:50,460
 koji ne mogu čuti inače u javnom životu.

1872
00:42:50,460 --> 00:42:51,860
 Dragi ljudi,

1873
00:42:51,860 --> 00:42:53,480
 profesor, doktor znanosti

1874
00:42:53,480 --> 00:42:54,980
 Josip Jurčević je to bio.

1875
00:42:54,980 --> 00:42:56,460
 Ja sam Marij Miletić.

1876
00:42:56,460 --> 00:42:57,840
 Hvala što ste me ovdje pratili

1877
00:42:57,840 --> 00:42:59,260
 i hvala što ste mi u Zboku.

